    "ingredients_source_text": "- 200 g (7 oz) green lentils - 50 g (1\u00be oz) vermicelli - 1 tsp curry powder - \u00bd tsp paprika powder - \u00bd tsp cinnamon powder - \u00bd tsp ground sumac",
